      "date": "2013-04-17 22:58:59.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n\"Jinshan, do you think it'd be possible to stop using LVB on the client side as well? (not in this patch, but at some point later)\"\n\nIf we decide to use an extra RPC to transfer layout for IT_LAYOUT, we don't need lock->l_lvb_data at all.",
